Notes:

1. The email must validated with the following regular expression: \w+@[a-z]+\.[a-z]{2,}
2. The dropdown should have the following options:
2.1 Standard: chocolate, vanilla, iogurt
2.2 Fruits: melon, mango, kiwi, strawberry
3. All inputs are mandatory, except the special requests section;
4. The password must have between 6 and 20 characters;
5. The special requests section cannot have more than 100 characters;
6. The 'Waffle cone' option must be disabled;
7. The 'Cup' option should be selected by default;